definitions.definition: A small village in Croft parish, Warrington borough , Cheshire , England ( OS grid ref SJ6295 ) .
A city in Goodhue County , Minnesota , United States .
A small village in Richmond , Washington County , Rhode Island , United States .
The former name of Pineridge , Fresno County , California .
